# MCP Tools: axiom

ALWAYS include `arguments` in CallMcpTool calls. NEVER send empty `{}`.

For Axiom data queries, discover datasets, metric names, tags, and fields before substantive queries. Use the narrowest useful `startTime` and `endTime`; every query scans data.

## Reporting Time Zone

- Axiom may return `_time` and RFC3339 timestamps in UTC. Keep query bounds in UTC or relative time when convenient, but convert every absolute timestamp and time range in user-facing reports to Singapore Time (`SGT`, `UTC+8`).
- Label reported times explicitly, for example `2026-07-10 23:05 SGT (UTC+8)`, and account for date rollover during conversion.
- Do not present raw UTC or `Z` timestamps in normal reports. If the user explicitly requests UTC, show it after the primary SGT value.

Zero-argument tools are intentionally skipped here: `listDatasets`, `listNotifiers`, `checkMonitors`, `listDashboards`, `getSavedQueries`.

### queryDataset
Query event, trace, and log datasets using APL. Do not use this for `otel-metrics-v1`; use `queryMetrics` instead.

| Field | Type | Required | Default | Description |
|-------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
| apl | string | Yes | - | APL query string |
| startTime | string | No | now-30m | Query range start as RFC3339 or relative time |
| endTime | string | No | now | Query range end as RFC3339 or relative time |

Example:
CallMcpTool({ server: "axiom", toolName: "queryDataset", arguments: { apl: "['logs'] | where ['_time'] > ago(5m) | take 10", startTime: "now-5m", endTime: "now" } })

### listMetrics
List available metric names and metadata in an `otel-metrics-v1` dataset.

| Field | Type | Required | Default | Description |
|-------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
| datasetName | string | Yes | - | Metrics dataset name |
| startTime | string | No | now-30m | Query range start as RFC3339 or relative time |
| endTime | string | No | now | Query range end as RFC3339 or relative time |

Example:
CallMcpTool({ server: "axiom", toolName: "listMetrics", arguments: { datasetName: "otel-metrics-v1", startTime: "now-3h", endTime: "now" } })

### searchMetrics
Search metric tag values for a known entity and return associated metric names.

| Field | Type | Required | Default | Description |
|-------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
| datasetName | string | Yes | - | Metrics dataset name |
| value | string | Yes | - | Exact entity/tag value to search for, such as service or host name |
| startTime | string | No | now-30m | Query range start; use at least `now-3h` for recent searchable data |
| endTime | string | No | now | Query range end as RFC3339 or relative time |

Example:
CallMcpTool({ server: "axiom", toolName: "searchMetrics", arguments: { datasetName: "otel-metrics-v1", value: "checkout-service", startTime: "now-3h", endTime: "now" } })

