### queryMetrics
Query OpenTelemetry metrics using MPL.

| Field | Type | Required | Default | Description |
|-------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
| mpl | string | Yes | - | MPL query string: `<dataset>:<metric> | <operations>` |
| datasetName | string | Yes | - | Metrics dataset name |
| startTime | string | No | now-30m | Query range start as RFC3339 or relative time |
| endTime | string | No | now | Query range end as RFC3339 or relative time |

Example:
CallMcpTool({ server: "axiom", toolName: "queryMetrics", arguments: { datasetName: "otel-metrics-v1", mpl: "`otel-metrics-v1`:`http.server.duration` | align to 5m using avg", startTime: "now-30m", endTime: "now" } })

### createNotifier
Create a notifier from a JSON payload.

| Field | Type | Required | Default | Description |
|-------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
| notifierJson | string | Yes | - | Full notifier JSON string with name and properties; configure one channel such as email, slack, webhook, customWebhook, pagerduty, opsgenie, discord, discordWebhook, or microsoftTeams |

Example:
CallMcpTool({ server: "axiom", toolName: "createNotifier", arguments: { notifierJson: "{\"name\":\"ops-email\",\"properties\":{\"email\":{\"emails\":[\"ops@example.com\"]}}}" } })

### updateNotifier
Update an existing notifier by ID using a full JSON payload.

| Field | Type | Required | Default | Description |
|-------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
| notifierId | string | Yes | - | Notifier ID from `listNotifiers` |
| notifierJson | string | Yes | - | Full notifier JSON string with name and properties |

Example:
CallMcpTool({ server: "axiom", toolName: "updateNotifier", arguments: { notifierId: "notifier-id", notifierJson: "{\"name\":\"ops-email\",\"properties\":{\"email\":{\"emails\":[\"ops@example.com\"]}}}" } })

### deleteNotifier
Delete a notifier by ID.

| Field | Type | Required | Default | Description |
|-------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
| notifierId | string | Yes | - | Notifier ID from `listNotifiers` |

Example:
CallMcpTool({ server: "axiom", toolName: "deleteNotifier", arguments: { notifierId: "notifier-id" } })

### createMonitor
Create a monitor from a JSON payload.

| Field | Type | Required | Default | Description |
|-------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
| monitorJson | string | Yes | - | Full monitor JSON string with name, type, intervalMinutes, rangeMinutes, notifierIds, and at least one of aplQuery or mplQuery |

Example:
CallMcpTool({ server: "axiom", toolName: "createMonitor", arguments: { monitorJson: "{\"name\":\"error-rate\",\"type\":\"Threshold\",\"intervalMinutes\":5,\"rangeMinutes\":15,\"notifierIds\":[],\"aplQuery\":\"['logs'] | summarize count()\"}" } })

