### createDashboard
Create a dashboard from a JSON document.

| Field | Type | Required | Default | Description |
|-------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
| dashboardJson | string | Yes | - | Full dashboard JSON string with required fields name, owner, charts, layout, refreshTime, schemaVersion, timeWindowStart, and timeWindowEnd |
| uid | string | No | - | Optional custom dashboard UID |
| message | string | No | - | Optional audit/change note |

Example:
CallMcpTool({ server: "axiom", toolName: "createDashboard", arguments: { dashboardJson: "{\"name\":\"Ops\",\"owner\":\"X-AXIOM-EVERYONE\",\"charts\":[],\"layout\":[],\"refreshTime\":60,\"schemaVersion\":2,\"timeWindowStart\":\"now-1h\",\"timeWindowEnd\":\"now\"}", message: "Create ops dashboard" } })

### getDashboard
Get dashboard details by UID.

| Field | Type | Required | Default | Description |
|-------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
| dashboardId | string | Yes | - | Dashboard UID from `listDashboards` |

Example:
CallMcpTool({ server: "axiom", toolName: "getDashboard", arguments: { dashboardId: "dashboard-uid" } })

### exportDashboard
Export a dashboard JSON document by UID.

| Field | Type | Required | Default | Description |
|-------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
| dashboardUid | string | Yes | - | Dashboard UID from `listDashboards` |

Example:
CallMcpTool({ server: "axiom", toolName: "exportDashboard", arguments: { dashboardUid: "dashboard-uid" } })

### updateDashboard
Update an existing dashboard by UID.

| Field | Type | Required | Default | Description |
|-------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
| dashboardUid | string | Yes | - | Dashboard UID from `listDashboards` |
| dashboardJson | string | Yes | - | Full dashboard JSON string |
| overwrite | boolean | No | true | If false, `version` is required for optimistic concurrency |
| version | number | No | - | Current dashboard version from `exportDashboard` |
| message | string | No | - | Optional audit/change note |

Example:
CallMcpTool({ server: "axiom", toolName: "updateDashboard", arguments: { dashboardUid: "dashboard-uid", dashboardJson: "{\"name\":\"Ops\",\"owner\":\"X-AXIOM-EVERYONE\",\"charts\":[],\"layout\":[],\"refreshTime\":60,\"schemaVersion\":2,\"timeWindowStart\":\"now-1h\",\"timeWindowEnd\":\"now\"}", overwrite: true } })

### updateDashboardChart
Patch a single chart in an existing dashboard.

| Field | Type | Required | Default | Description |
|-------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
| dashboardUid | string | Yes | - | Dashboard UID from `listDashboards` |
| chartId | string | Yes | - | Chart ID inside the dashboard charts array |
| chartPatchJson | string | Yes | - | JSON merge-patch object for a single chart |
| overwrite | boolean | No | true | If false, `version` is required for optimistic concurrency |
| version | number | No | - | Current dashboard version from `exportDashboard` |
| message | string | No | - | Optional audit/change note |

Example:
CallMcpTool({ server: "axiom", toolName: "updateDashboardChart", arguments: { dashboardUid: "dashboard-uid", chartId: "chart-id", chartPatchJson: "{\"title\":\"Latency p95\"}", overwrite: true } })

### deleteDashboard
Delete a dashboard by UID.

| Field | Type | Required | Default | Description |
|-------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
| dashboardUid | string | Yes | - | Dashboard UID from `listDashboards` |

Example:
CallMcpTool({ server: "axiom", toolName: "deleteDashboard", arguments: { dashboardUid: "dashboard-uid" } })
